name: Cedra Network
description: Cedra is the first community-owned blockchain built on the Move language that lets anyone spin up and govern their own sovereign networks. Designed as a public good, Cedra fuses protocol development, funding, and growth into open collaboration among core contributors, a non-profit foundation, and a worldwide guild of builders. Cedra is part of a new wave of community led distributed systems where funding, development, and growth are done in collaboration with core contributors, builders, and a global network of token holders
